      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wihrī iṣgabje/ un ar Joabu ka-\\\nwaḥs/ tad kritte zitti no teem\\\nLaudim/ un no Dahwida Kal-\\\npeem/ un Urijas tas Eetiteris no-\\\nmirre arridsan.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fuhttija Joabs/ un\\\ndewe Dahwidam Sinnu no wiṣ-\\\nfahni Karru Leetahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiṣsch pawehleja tam\\\nWehstnescham/ un fazzija: Rad\\\ntu beigst wiṣṣas Karru Leetas tam\\\nKehninam stahstihṭ/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Kehninsch apskai-\\\ntifsees/ un us tew fazzihṣ: Ka-\\\npehz effat juhstik tuwu pee Pils-\\\ntahta nahkuṣchi fautees? ne sin-\\\nnajat juhs ta mehds no Muhra\\\nschaudihṭ?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kaṣ irr Abimeleku Jerub-\\\nBāāla Dehtu kavis? Neggi\\\nweena Seewa weenu Dsirnu-Ak-\\\nmixa Gabbalu us winnu mette\\\nno ta Muhra/ ka tas Teebezāno-\\\nmirre? kapehz effat juhs tik tu-\\\nwu pee Muhra nahkuṣchi? tad\\\nfakki tu: Taws Kalps Urijas tas\\\nEetiteris irr arridsan nomirris.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Wehstnefis nogah-\\\nje/ un nahze/ un stahstija Dah-\\\nwidam wiṣṣu/ par ko Joabs win-\\\nxu bij fuhtijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Wehstnetis fazzi-\\\nja us Dahwidu: Tee Wihrī bi-\\\nja stipraki ne ka mehs/ un iṣgah-\\\nje prett mums us Laukn/ bet\\\nmehs turrejamess winxeem pret-\\\nti lihds paṣchahni Wahrtu Dur-\\\nwim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad schaudija tee Strehl-\\\nneeki no Muhra us tawecin Kal-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un taws Kalps Urijas\\\ntas Eetiteris irr arridsan nomir-\\\nris. Tad fazzija Dahwids us to\\\nWehstnesi: Ta buhs tew us Jo-\\\nabu fazzihṭ: Laid tew fchi Leeta\\\nnetabbi ne patihk/ jo tas Soh-\\\nbins riḥj drihs scho/ drihs zittu/\\\nstiprinti tawu Karru prett to Pils-\\\ntahtu/ un tspohstt to/ un ta ee-\\\ndrohfchina winnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rad nu Urijafa Seewa\\\ndsirdeja/ ka winnas Wihrs Uri-\\\njas bija nomirris/ tad schehlo-\\\njahṣ winna pahr sawu Kungu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad tas Schchlescha-\\\nnas Laiks bija pagahjis/ nosuhti\\\nja Dahwids/ un nehme to sawu\\\nNamnā/ un ta tappe winnan\\\npar Seewu/ un dseindeja win-\\\nnam weenu Dehtu: Bet fchi Lee\\\nta/ ko Dahwids darrija/ ne po\\\ntikke tam KUNGAM.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "peem/ ka zittino ta Rehnina Kal-\\\npeem nomirre.\n"
    }
  ],
